Fixed git-arch to accept revspec argument.

Previously git-arch only worked on implicit symbolic-ref HEAD or detached HEAD.
Now accepts a revspec parameter to specify which ref to create archive tags for.

Usage examples:
- git arch (archives current HEAD)
- git arch master (archives master branch)
- git arch abc123 (archives specific commit)

Renamed TARGET variable to refname for clarity.

/Claude-haiku@4.5
